### Scenario: Health check endpoint available
```gherkin
Given a running BFF server
When a client requests GET /health
Then a JSON response with status "healthy" is returned
  And the response includes name and version
```

### Scenario: Docker build succeeds
```gherkin
Given a BFF project with valid configuration
When `docker build -t my-bff .` is executed
Then the Docker image builds successfully
  And the image runs and responds on configured port
